description: U.S. Energy Initiatives Corporation Inc., together with its subsidiaries, focuses on MJ and green energy businesses in California. It engages in crypto currency and cannabis operations. The company was formerly known as Hybrid Fuel Systems, Inc. and changed its name to U.S. Energy Initiatives Corporation Inc. in June 2006. U.S. Energy Initiatives Corporation Inc. was founded in 1996 and is based in Woodland Hills, California.
